    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Franklin Titus</b>\n</p><p><b>Franklin Titus</b> (kingliveson) <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>,<br />\na computer chess aficionado and programmer, <a href=\"/Category:Opening_Book_Author\" title=\"Category:Opening Book Author\">opening book author</a>, \nexpert of the <a href=\"/Ippolit\" title=\"Ippolit\">Ippolit</a> family of engines, hosting <a href=\"/RobboLito\" title=\"RobboLito\">RobboLito</a> and <a href=\"/IvanHoe\" title=\"IvanHoe\">IvanHoe</a> sources and executables, as well as various <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">endgame tablebases</a> and <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">opening books</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \nFranklin Titus was early critic of <a href=\"/Robert_Houdart\" title=\"Robert Houdart\">Robert Houdart</a> concerning <a href=\"/Houdini\" title=\"Houdini\">Houdini</a> and its apparent RobboLito origins <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \nHe was active poster in <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a> until mid 2010, and since then in <a href=\"/Jeremy_Bernstein\" title=\"Jeremy Bernstein\">Jeremy Bernstein's</a> <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2009\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2009</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Franklin_Titus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2009\">2009</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Franklin_Titus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2009\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30906\">Chessbase Promoting RobboLito?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 02, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/RobboLito\" title=\"RobboLito\">RobboLito</a>, <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31392\">Book: KLO 150 ECO A00-E97 Variations</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 31, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Franklin_Titus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31701\">Ivan The Terrible</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 14, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/IvanHoe\" title=\"IvanHoe\">IvanHoe</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=171\">Material/Mobility</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, June 17, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Influence_Quantity_of_Pieces\" title=\"Influence Quantity of Pieces\">Influence Quantity of Pieces</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=588\">Move on Hash Hit</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, August 18, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Time_Management\" title=\"Time Management\">Time Management</a>, <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">Pondering</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2011</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=1072\">ь code</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, February 03, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Ippolit\" title=\"Ippolit\">Ippolit</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=1587\">GPL Question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, September 02, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=1592\">IPON Rating's List Bash Script</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, September 05, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/IPON\" title=\"IPON\">IPON</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=1647\">Computer Chess Biggest Liar</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, October 09, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Houdini\" title=\"Houdini\">Houdini</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2012</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=1771\">ChessBase: A Gross Miscarriage of Justice in Computer Chess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 02, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Rybka_Controversy\" title=\"Rybka Controversy\">Rybka Controversy</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=1856\">Zugzwang Collection</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, February 14, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Test-Positions\" title=\"Test-Positions\">Test-Positions</a>, <a href=\"/Zugzwang\" title=\"Zugzwang\">Zugzwang</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Franklin_Titus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=3039\">Fixed: Corrupted tablebases archive @ chess.cygnitec.com</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, November 19, 2016</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Franklin_Titus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chess.cygnitec.com/\">cygnitec</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chess.cygnitec.com/engine/ivanhoe/\">Index of /engine/ivanhoe</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://chess.cygnitec.com/engine/robbolito/\">Index of /engine/robbolito</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">kingliveson</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Franklin_Titus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://computer-chess.org/forum/index.php?mode=thread&amp;id=1080\">Computer-Chess